1. Install Python 2.6. It should work on other versions of Python, but it has
   only been tested on this version so far.

2. Install MySQL <http://dev.mysql.com/downloads/>

3. Install Tornado <http://www.tornadoweb.org/>

4. Install httplib2 <http://code.google.com/p/httplib2/>

5. Install iso8601 <http://pypi.python.org/pypi/iso8601>

6. Install oz <http://github.com/ysimonson/oz/>

7. Install scarecrow <http://github.com/ysimonson/scarecrow>

8. Create a new database in MySQL

9. Configure your database settings in settings/blackbox.py

10. Run setup:
      python setup.py blackbox db testusers
    This will initialize the database schema and add the users for testing

11. Run the server:
      python setup.py blackbox -dbpass
    Enter your database password. The server is now running!